Server and example Client for "mex" game,
used for student projects in software engineering,

http://www.imn.htwk-leipzig.de/~waldmann/edu/ws11/st/folien/main/node79.html

(c) Johannes Waldmann, 2012

See INSTALL for instructions. --- Example usage:

# start the server in the background,
# arguments: port number, passwd file name
mex-server 2012 passwd &

# start one client,  arguments: 
# user name, password, client port, server URL
mex-client A A 3000 http://localhost:2012/rpc &

# start another client (use different name and port)
mex-client B B 3001 http://localhost:2012/rpc &

# then the server will start games.
# watch system state at  http://localhost:2012/log


